print('Similarly, this is where the line [y = 2x -2] intercept the X-axis\nat y =0')
print('Therefore from: y = 2x -2\n==0  = 2(x) -2 (where y=0)\n==0  = 2x - 2\n==2x = 2;\nTherefore the line the X-intercept = 1 @ coordinates [0,-2]')
